sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant C as CLI Client
    participant D as Daemon
    participant W as Worker Pool
    participant IPC as Unix Socket
    participant S as State Store
    participant L as Log

    U->>C: stop
    C->>D: ShutdownRequest
    D->>D: set shutting_down=true
    D->>L: log shutdown started
    D->>IPC: stop accepting new add
    D->>W: wait running jobs (grace period)
    alt all jobs finished in time
        W-->>D: workers idle
    else timeout
        D->>W: terminate remaining workers
    end
    D->>S: flush state
    D->>IPC: close and unlink socket
    D->>L: log shutdown completed
    D-->>C: ShutdownAck
    C-->>U: daemon stopped